    "Therefore, any policy framework must prioritize intent-based regulation, investment in cross-sector R&D, and transparency-by-design.",
    "As the information environment grows more complex, building a layered, adaptive, and evidence-based response that leverages the full spectrum of AI capabilities is the only viable path forward.",
